2
00:00:06,560 --> 00:00:09,410
something called the WHO&#39;s framework

3
00:00:09,410 --> 00:00:11,800
for data quality review.

4
00:00:11,800 --> 00:00:14,090
This is an approach to assessing

5
00:00:14,090 --> 00:00:16,250
the quality of the data,

6
00:00:16,250 --> 00:00:18,160
which are routinely reported

7
00:00:18,160 --> 00:00:20,423
by health facilities each month.

8
00:00:22,610 --> 00:00:24,610
There are a variety of tools

9
00:00:24,610 --> 00:00:28,490
that you may be familiar with for assessing data quality.

10
00:00:28,490 --> 00:00:30,750
Here are several of them.

11
